text: René Ostertag (4 May 1926 – 17 October 2022) was a French cyclist. Ostertag was active from the 1940s to the 1960s. He had about 350 victories. In 2020, he published a book about his cycling career. Ostertag died on 17 October 2022, aged 96. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:French cyclists Category:1926 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Sportspeople from Paris Category:Place of death missing
